		(l)	Reference to “section I.D, greenhouse gas inventory information, of the guidelines for the preparation of the information required under Article 7” in paragraph 51 of the annex to decision 22/CMP.1 shall be read as reference to “guidance included in annex II to decision 2/CMP.8 and in decision 6/CMP.9”;
		(m)	Reference to “section I.E of the annex to decision 15/CMP.1” in paragraphs 88(a) and 93 of the annex to decision 22/CMP.1 shall be read as a reference to “guidance included in section I.E of the annex to decision 15/CMP.1 and in annex III to decision 
3/CMP.11”;
